<doc f='codebrowser/src/entities/Hero.cpp' l='1152'>/**
 * \brief Updates the hero depending on its movement.
 *
 * This function is called when the hero&apos;s movement direction changes (for instance
 * because the player pressed or released a directional key, or the hero just reached an obstacle).
 * It updates the hero&apos;s animations and collisions according to the new movement.
